casebody.head_matter:
Rubin R. WEEKS, Petitioner
v.
Jason LEWIS, Warden
No. 19-5519
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
